00:06:50.160 --> 00:06:52.880
Ini.. Bagaimana ini bisa muncul di TV?

00:06:53.120 --> 00:06:55.120
Durva, apakah itu
terhubung ke ponselmu?

00:06:55.320 --> 00:06:57.600
Tolong matikan.  - Kakak ipar..

00:06:58.480 --> 00:07:00.880
